title: Top 100 Country Singles of 2014
description:
JASON ALDEAN has the number one country song for 2014 with When She Says Baby. The year-end chart includes all singles from Nov 10, 2013 to Nov 08, 2014 and ranked by Mediabase. LUKE BRYAN, however, was the most played artist (no surprise considering he had 4 entries last year), followed by BLAKE SHELTON at number 2 and then FLORIDA-GEORGIA LINE in the third position.
